data.meta_description: 2,821 likes, 44 comments - jayblakesberg on November 13, 2023: "Happy Birthday Neil Young. Born November 12, 1945. So much can be said about Neil and his music and vibe but i’m just gonna let the pictures speak…if you want to hear Neil stories i’ll be at the Contemporary Jewish Museum in SF this Sunday 11/19 at 1:30pm doing a walking tour of the RetroBlakesberg exhibition. #neilyoung @neilyoungarchives @jewseum".
